Points" for a <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$23 million</NUMEX> Harrier <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">fighter jet</ENAMEX>. No reasonable <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">person</ENAMEX> would
believe it, she said. In <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1996</TIMEX> the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">chairman</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">Republican National</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Committee, Haley Barbour</ENAMEX>, promised <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$1 million</NUMEX> to any <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> who proved that a
