<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Twenty</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Americans</ENAMEX> filed breach of contract suits. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">A dozen</NUMEX> are still litigating.
The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">RNC</ENAMEX> has already settled with <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> claimant for an undisclosed amount. Last
<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">year</TIMEX> talking-head <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">lawyer</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Joseph DiGenova</ENAMEX> got <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NBC</ENAMEX> to fork up <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$10,000</NUMEX> after
